1- Expense List( amount, date(user adds),category name, description(not required)


2- Category List (name-from database)


3- Form: New Expense (
  amount (required),
  date (required),
  category (required, dropdown from Category List),
  description (optional)
)
-After save, new Expense form is reopened


4- Form: New Category (
  name (required) - save to database
)


5- Summary View:
[Category Name] / [Total Amount]